   "id": "theoretical-foundation",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 🧭 Cross-Absolute Selection Principle (CASP)\n",
    "\n",
    "## 📜 Formal Definition\n",
    "\n",
    "> **Definition (CASP):** A mediated interaction between two Absolute Entities is valid if and only if it minimizes the cross-absolute interaction action, maintains entropic compatibility within tolerance δ, and maximizes directional coherence, subject to irreducibility constraints.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Ontological Context\n",
    "**Builds directly on:** `05_transfinite_interaction_chains.ipynb`\n",
    "\n",
    "### Preceding Theoretical Framework\n",
    "This notebook extends the **Enhanced Mathematical Ontology of Absolute Nothingness**, providing a rigorous formalization of cross-absolute interactions.\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 🔷 Theoretical Foundations\n",
    "\n",
    "### Transfinite Interaction Chains (TIC) Constraint\n",
    "All CASP evaluations are subordinate to the entropy trajectory constraint:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$ \\varepsilon_{n+1} \\geq \\varepsilon_n $$\n",
    "\n",
    "### Entropy Conservation and Legality\n",
    "Interaction permissibility is determined by entropy leak:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$ \\delta = \\frac{\\Delta\\varepsilon}{\\varepsilon_1} $$\n",
    "\n",
    "Interaction is legal only if $\\delta \\leq 10^{-6}$\n",
    "\n",
    "### Core Postulates\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Postulate I: Minimal Interaction Action\n",
    "$$ \\mathcal{A}_{\\text{min}} = \\arg \\min_{M \\in \\mathcal{M}} \\| S_1 M S_2^T \\|_F $$\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Postulate II: Entropic Compatibility\n",
    "$$ \\Delta \\varepsilon = |\\varepsilon_1 - \\mathrm{Tr}(I I^T)| < \\delta_\\text{tolerance} $$\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Postulate III: Directional Coherence Maximization\n",
    "$$ \\max \\left( \\langle S_1 M, S_2 \\rangle \\right) $$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "imports-and-setup",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Comprehensive Scientific Computing Imports\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "import scipy.optimize as optimize\n",
    "import sympy as sp\n",
    "\n",
    "# Advanced Configuration\n",
    "np.random.seed(42)\n",
    "plt.style.use('seaborn-v0_8-whitegrid')\n",
    "np.set_printoptions(precision=6, suppress=True)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "absolute-entity-class",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "class CASPViolation(Exception):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Exception raised for violations of Cross-Absolute Selection Principle\"\"\"\n",
    "    pass\n",
    "\n",
    "class AbsoluteEntity:\n",
    "    \"\"\"Rigorous representation of an Absolute Entity with comprehensive constraints\"\"\"\n",
    "    def __init__(self, signature, state, tolerance=1e-6):\n",
    "        # Rigorous validation of signature and state\n",
    "        assert signature.shape[0] == signature.shape[1], \"Signature must be square\"\n",
    "        assert np.allclose(signature, signature.T), \"Signature must be symmetric\"\n",
    "        assert state.shape[0] == signature.shape[0], \"State dimension mismatch\"\n",
    "        \n",
    "        self.signature = signature\n",
    "        self.state = state\n",
    "        self.entropy = np.trace(signature @ signature.T)\n",
    "        self.tolerance = tolerance\n",
    "    \n",
    "    def validate_interaction(self, other, mediator):\n",
    "        \"\"\"Check interaction validity according to CASP\"\"\"\n",
    "        results = evaluate_casp(self, other, mediator)\n",
    "        if (results['EntropyLeak'] > self.tolerance) or (results['CoherenceIndex'] < 0):\n",
    "            raise CASPViolation(f\"Invalid interaction: {results}\")\n",
    "        return results"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "mediator-construction",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def construct_mediator(a_dim, b_dim, complexity=0.5, seed=None):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Advanced mediator construction with complexity-based projection\"\"\"\n",
    "    rng = np.random.default_rng(seed)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Complexity-weighted random matrix generation\n",
    "    M = rng.normal(0, complexity, (a_dim, b_dim))\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # QR decomposition for orthonormalization\n",
    "    Q, _ = np.linalg.qr(M)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return Q[:, :b_dim]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "id": "casp-evaluation",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def cosine_similarity(a, b):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Normalized cosine similarity between vectors\"\"\"\n",
    "    return np.dot(a, b) / (np.linalg.norm(a) * np.linalg.norm(b))\n",
    "\n",
    "def evaluate_casp(entity_a, entity_b, mediator):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Comprehensive CASP evaluation\"\"\"\n",
    "    I = entity_a.signature @ mediator @ entity_b.signature.T\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Interaction Action (Frobenius Norm)\n",
    "    action = np.linalg.norm(I, ord='fro')\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Entropy Gap and Leak\n",
    "    trace_proj = np.trace(I @ I.T)\n",
    "    entropy_gap = abs(entity_a.entropy - trace_proj)\n",
    "    entropy_leak = entropy_gap / entity_a.entropy\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Normalized Directional Coherence\n",
    "    projected_a = (entity_a.signature @ mediator).flatten()\n",
    "    state_b = entity_b.signature.flatten()\n",
    "    coherence_index = cosine_similarity(projected_a, state_b)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # State Vector Interaction Term\n",
    "    state_interaction = np.dot(entity_a.state, mediator.T @ entity_b.state)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Interaction Classification\n",
    "    if entropy_leak <= 1e-6 and coherence_index > 0:\n",
    "        interaction_type = \"Resonant Convergence\"\n",
    "    elif entropy_leak > 1e-6:\n",
    "        interaction_type = \"Entropic Conflict\"\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        interaction_type = \"Directional Collapse\"\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return {\n",
    "        'InteractionAction': action,\n",
    "        'EntropyGap': entropy_gap,\n",
    "        'EntropyLeak': entropy_leak,\n",
    "        'CoherenceIndex': coherence_index,\n",
    "        'StateInteraction': state_interaction,\n",
    "        'InteractionType': interaction_type,\n",
    "        'InformationTensor': I\n",
    "    }"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "id": "optimization-framework",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def optimize_casp_mediator(entity_a, entity_b, initial_guess=None):\n",
    "    \"\"\"CASP-Compliant Mediator Optimization\"\"\"\n",
    "    dim = entity_a.signature.shape[0]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    def objective(M_flat):\n",
    "        M = M_flat.reshape((dim, dim))\n",
    "        results = evaluate_casp(entity_a, entity_b, M)\n",
    "        return results['InteractionAction']\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Initial mediator if not provided\n",
    "    if initial_guess is None:\n",
    "        initial_guess = construct_mediator(dim, dim)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Optimize using L-BFGS method\n",
    "    result = optimize.minimize(\n",
    "        objective, \n",
    "        initial_guess.flatten(), \n",
    "        method='L-BFGS-B'\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return result.x.reshape((dim, dim))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "id": "simulation-and-analysis",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "🔬 CASP Interaction Analysis:\n",
      "Interaction Type: Resonant Convergence\n",
      "Interaction Action: 1.424215\n",
      "Entropy Leak: 0.000000\n",
      "Coherence Index: 0.222942\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Comprehensive Simulation\n",
    "np.random.seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Generate Absolute Entities\n",
    "A_sig = np.random.rand(4, 4)\n",
    "A_sig = 0.5 * (A_sig + A_sig.T)  # Symmetric\n",
    "B_sig = np.random.rand(4, 4)\n",
    "B_sig = 0.5 * (B_sig + B_sig.T)  # Symmetric\n",
    "\n",
    "A = AbsoluteEntity(A_sig, np.random.rand(4))\n",
    "B = AbsoluteEntity(B_sig, np.random.rand(4))\n",
    "\n",
    "# Optimize Mediator\n",
    "M_optimized = optimize_casp_mediator(A, B)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Evaluate Interaction\n",
    "results = evaluate_casp(A, B, M_optimized)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Detailed Results\n",
    "print(\"🔬 CASP Interaction Analysis:\")\n",
    "print(f\"Interaction Type: {results['InteractionType']}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Interaction Action: {results['InteractionAction']:.6f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Entropy Leak: {results['EntropyLeak']:.6f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Coherence Index: {results['CoherenceIndex']:.6f}\")"
   ]
  },
